<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-5279] camel-stream overwrites files instead of appending</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-5279</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When a file stream is used with camel-stream, the file is not opened in append mode, therefore the file is overwritten with every message, ending up with just the last message, all others are lost.&lt;/p&gt;

